<task id="004" project="sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix">
  <metadata>
    <title>Coordinate with `sdap-bff-api-and-performance-enhancement-r1` (UQ-03)</title>
    <status>not-started</status>
    <estimated-effort>30 minutes</estimated-effort>
    <assigned>Project owner</assigned>
    <started></started>
    <completed></completed>
    <tags>coordination, phase-0</tags>
    <parallel-group>A</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>true</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Independent owner coordination ask</parallel-reason>
    <rigor>STANDARD</rigor>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    Confirm with the `sdap-bff-api-and-performance-enhancement-r1` project owner whether that
    project is deploying any BFF changes in the next 6 weeks. This project's Phase 4 needs a
    clean baseline and cannot have in-flight BFF deploys from siblings mid-bake.
  </prompt>

  <role>Project coordinator.</role>

  <goal>
    Documented decision: either (a) no in-flight deploys expected in Phase 4 window, or
    (b) coordination plan to sequence deploys to avoid Phase 4 contention.
  </goal>

  <inputs>
    <file purpose="design-spec">projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/design.md</file>
    <file purpose="sibling-project">projects/sdap-bff-api-and-performance-enhancement-r1/</file>
  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="design.md §2.3">Confirm with owner that no overlapping changes are mid-deploy at Phase 4 kickoff</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>projects/sdap-bff-api-and-performance-enhancement-r1/README.md</file>
      <file>projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/design.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <context>
    <background>
      The perf enhancement project (~124–170h scope: Redis, Dataverse perf, resilience, AI pipeline
      perf) is orthogonal in scope but both touch BFF. Co-deploy risk is LOW but mid-bake deploy by
      a sibling would invalidate Phase 4 observation windows.
    </background>
    <dependencies>
      <dependency task="001" status="not-started">Owner sign-off required first</dependency>
    </dependencies>
  </context>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Contact `sdap-bff-api-and-performance-enhancement-r1` owner</step>
    <step order="2">Confirm whether any BFF deploys are expected in next 6 weeks</step>
    <step order="3">If YES: develop deploy-sequencing plan; document in CLAUDE.md</step>
    <step order="4">If NO: document confirmation in CLAUDE.md Decisions Made</step>
    <step order="5">Update Phase 0 checklist item 3 to checked</step>
    <step order="6">Update TASK-INDEX.md status of task 004 from 🔲 to ✅</step>
  </steps>

  <tools><tool name="git">Update CLAUDE.md + task index</tool></tools>

  <outputs>
    <output type="docs">projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/CLAUDE.md (Decisions Made entry)</output>
    <output type="docs">projects/sdap-bff-api-remediation-fix/tasks/TASK-INDEX.md (status update)</output>
  </outputs>

  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">UQ-03 answer recorded in CLAUDE.md</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Phase 0 checklist item 3 marked complete</criterion>
  </acceptance-criteria>
</task>
